## PROHIBITED Architectural Patterns

❌ **Direct Component Communication**: Must communicate through orchestrator  
❌ **Bypassing Registration**: All components must register with orchestrator  
❌ **Independent Trading**: All trades require RiskManager authorization (Rule 3)  
❌ **Skipping Regime Context**: Cannot process signals without regime awareness  
❌ **Direct Database Access**: Must use ClickHouseDataManager (Rule 2)  
❌ **Strategy Isolation**: Strategies must coordinate through StrategyManager (Rule 3)  
❌ **Unmanaged Lifecycle**: All components must implement ISystemComponent  
❌ **Scattered Configs**: Don't define configs outside `core_engine/config/`  
❌ **Hardcoded Defaults**: Don't embed config values in component code  

